cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is about improving neural machine translation for low-resource language pairs using transfer learning. The main focus is on natural language processing (NLP), which falls under the category of cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves training neural networks, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the use of Byte Pair Encoding (BPE) could be related to computer vision (cs.CV) or neural networks (cs.NE).
